ygData.messageBody:
The subject of highpass brough something from the back of my mind: once when i
was searching through the upper part of the castle i desovered many locked secret
doors, ie.. a plain wall that I barely walk through only to see a door that won't
budge. This may be an interesting subject for thieves with lockpicking to
explore. Also I was wondering of any quests in highpass. Lasty has anyone been
down into the dungeon area of highkeep? The first sentry monster I conned was red
to a 17th level character. This is the area past the man that sell smithing raw
materials down near the bank, not in the prison area however. Also If you are of
good alignment don't talk to prisoners they will kill on talk and they can leave
there cells and gaurds will not kill them. They are similar in look to the madmen
of RO. Oh, and has anyone gambled at the 100pp minumum table in the casino in
highkeep?


Thanks in advance.

mithe of cathic-thule
